Package: pathwayPCM
Type: Package
Title: Phylogenetic Comparative Modeling of Macroevolutionary Pathways
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Takao K.",
           family = "Suzuki",
           email = "xxx@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for reconstructing macroevolutionary pathways of trait combinations 
    using the Bayesian framework of BayesTraits. Provides functions for 
    data formatting, model execution, and visualization of evolutionary transition networks.
